




{"id":11458,"date":"2022-08-24T09:14:15","date_gmt":"2022-08-24T02:14:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=11458"},"modified":"2022-08-24T09:14:15","modified_gmt":"2022-08-24T02:14:15","slug":"tim-hieu-ve-man-hinh-cam-ung-kiosk","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tim-hieu-ve-man-hinh-cam-ung-kiosk\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng Kiosk"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_78 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">N\u1ed9i dung ch\u00ednh<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tim-hieu-ve-man-hinh-cam-ung-kiosk\/#man_hinh_cam_ung_kiosk_la_gi\" >M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng Kiosk l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tim-hieu-ve-man-hinh-cam-ung-kiosk\/#tai_sao_man_hinh_cam_ung_kiosk_lai_quan_trong\" >T\u1ea1i sao m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng Kiosk l\u1ea1i quan tr\u1ecdng?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng Kiosk \u0111ang gia t\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao. C\u00e1c M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng Kiosk cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng Kiosk v\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao xu h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u00fang kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"man_hinh_cam_ung_kiosk_la_gi\"><\/span>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng Kiosk l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng kiosk cho ph\u00e9p t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t, ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ho\u1eb7c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh, ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 ng\u00f3n tay ho\u1eb7c b\u00fat stylus.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1c kiost m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c kiost truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, t\u0129nh ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3, v\u00ec ch\u00fang cho ph\u00e9p t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cao h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1c kiost m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb th\u00f4ng tin, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, li\u00ean l\u1ea1c quan tr\u1ecdng, ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i v\u00e9 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 thanh to\u00e1n \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed.<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c kiost n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t WiFi, cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb xa v\u00e0 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m, gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u00e1c kiost m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh cho m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-11462 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-24-at-09.02.41-1-469x400.png\" alt=\"M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng Kiosk l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\" width=\"469\" height=\"400\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-24-at-09.02.41-1-469x400.png 469w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-24-at-09.02.41-1-768x655.png 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-24-at-09.02.41-1-600x512.png 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-24-at-09.02.41-1.png 818w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai_sao_man_hinh_cam_ung_kiosk_lai_quan_trong\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ea1i sao m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng Kiosk l\u1ea1i quan tr\u1ecdng?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>C\u00e1c kiost m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch truy c\u1eadp v\u00ec ch\u00fang cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ngu\u1ed3n nh\u00e2n l\u1ef1c c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n. C\u00e1c m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng Kiosk th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t \u1edf nh\u1eefng khu v\u1ef1c thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 truy c\u1eadp, theo m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<p>V\u00ec ki-\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n l\u00e0 m\u00e1y t\u00ednh chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t cho m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho ph\u00e9p ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan.\u00a0Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a kiosk l\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p c\u01a1 s\u1edf d\u1eef li\u1ec7u th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng truy c\u1eadp<\/p>\n<p>KIOSK th\u00f4ng tin s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p quy\u1ec1n truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0o th\u00f4ng tin cho m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch giao ti\u1ebfp, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed ho\u1eb7c gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ki \u1ed1t n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c ki \u1ed1t kh\u00e1c \u1edf ch\u1ed7 n\u00f3 cung c\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng truy c\u1eadp. B\u1ea3o t\u00e0ng, c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c gia, th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u00e2n bay l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e1c ki-\u1ed1t th\u00f4ng tin.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-11460 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-24-at-09.02.21-402x400.png\" alt=\"T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng Kiosk\" width=\"402\" height=\"400\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-24-at-09.02.21-402x400.png 402w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-24-at-09.02.21-280x280.png 280w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-24-at-09.02.21-100x100.png 100w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-24-at-09.02.21-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-24-at-09.02.21-600x597.png 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-24-at-09.02.21.png 706w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 402px) 100vw, 402px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c 49 inch Inno<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>T\u00edch h\u1ee3p t\u00ednh n\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf sang tr\u1ecdng, si\u00eau m\u1ecfng<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i Full HD s\u1eafc n\u00e9t<\/li>\n<li>Hi\u0300nh a\u0309nh mu\u031b\u01a1\u0323t ma\u0300, ma\u0300u s\u0103\u0301c s\u00f4\u0301ng \u0111\u1ecd\u0302ng.<\/li>\n<li>Co\u0301 kha\u0309 na\u0306ng ch\u00f4\u0301ng la\u0323i nguy co\u031b nhi\u00ea\u0303u t\u01b0\u0300 a\u0301nh sa\u0301ng t\u01b0\u0323 nhie\u0302n va\u0300 mo\u0302i tru\u031b\u01a1\u0300ng xung quanh.<\/li>\